Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:39.40,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}会一直埋藏于我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:44.99,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}Don't cry  这是彼此的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:53.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}一起共同进退  没必要独自流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:03:03.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}只有能互相分担悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:07.43,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}就能够变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:15.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}马上绽放笑容吧  My friend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:23.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(100,200)\blur3}从心底笑出来  不必为谁而笑
